benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: POST /1.0/kb/invoicePayments/{paymentId}/tags - Add tags to payment

covered: POST Valid Payload: Successful addition of tags (TC01, TC02, TC03).
POST Invalid Payload: Handles malformed JSON, invalid tag UUIDs, extra fields, malicious input, and partial input (TC08, TC09, TC10, TC16, TC17).
POST Duplicate Submission / Idempotency: Duplicate tag definitions handled and idempotent (TC11, TC19).
POST Large Payloads / Performance: Large payloads and heavy-load scenarios (TC12, TC14).
POST Error Handling: Service unavailable scenario (TC13).
POST Non-Existing Resource & Bad Input Errors: 404 for missing payment (TC05, TC18); 400 for invalid paymentId format (TC06) and missing header (TC07).
POST Authorization / Security: Unauthorized user test (TC15).
